 U.S. President Thomas Wilson that the crust of the earth is becoming unstable and that without proper preparations for saving a fraction of the world's population, the entire race is doomed. Meanwhile, writer Jackson Curtis stumbles on the same information. While the world's leaders race to build \"arks\" to escape the impending cataclysm, Curtis struggles to find a way to save his family. Meanwhile, volcanic eruptions and earthquakes of unprecedented strength wreak havoc around the world.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":11.4787,"vote_count":12553,"poster_path":"/c2PkTPT5D9zB8SIm5wNlDAANEqM.jpg","release_date":"2009-10-10","vote_average":5.868,"backdrop_path":"/jCvkDqWWBrgxf9R3DrtJ6GpqXse.jpg","original_title":"2012","original_language":"en"},{"id":13475,"adult":false,"title":"Star Trek","video":false,"overview":"The fate of the galaxy rests in the hands of bitter rivals. One, James Kirk, is a delinquent, thrill-seeking Iowa farm boy. The other, Spock, a Vulcan, was raised in a logic-based society that rejects all emotion. As fiery instinct clashes with calm reason, their unlikely but powerful partnership is the only thing capable of leading their crew through unimaginable danger, boldly going where no one has gone before. The human adventure has begun again.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.6182,"vote_count":10333,"poster_path":"/hN2ZtF3Uw6mhIHZiqL0SKzELtKn.jpg","release_date":"2009-05-06","vote_average":7.429,"backdrop_path":"/cqXEwYFcwyKPZCKl1jAPaG3cMsl.jpg","original_title":"Star Trek","original_language":"en"},{"id":2080,"adult":false,"title":"X-Men Origins: Wolverine","video":false,"overview":"After seeking to live a normal life, Logan sets out to avenge the death of his girlfriend by undergoing the mutant Weapon X program and becoming Wolverine.","genre_ids":[12,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8186,"vote_count":11085,"poster_path":"/yj8LbTju1p7CUJg7US2unSBk33s.jpg","release_date":"2009-04-28"