":"Skipper, Kowalski, Rico and Private join forces with undercover organization The North Wind to stop the villainous Dr. Octavius Brine from destroying the world as we know it.","genre_ids":[10751,16,12,35],"popularity":7.6,"vote_count":4402,"poster_path":"/dXbpNrPDZDMEbujFoOxmMNQVMHa.jpg","release_date":"2014-11-22","vote_average":6.53,"backdrop_path":"/2QMgoiDlTmrO9FngZft8GgZ2SbX.jpg","original_title":"Penguins of Madagascar","original_language":"en"},{"id":1656,"adult":false,"title":"The Legend of Zorro","video":false,"overview":"Despite trying to keep his swashbuckling to a minimum, a threat to California's pending statehood causes the adventure-loving Don Alejandro de la Vega and his wife, Elena, to take action.","genre_ids":[28,12,37],"popularity":3.1451,"vote_count":3041,"poster_path":"/duZDsuIA2uX93Vujtm89oHeTFqE.jpg","release_date":"2005-10-24","vote_average":6.12,"backdrop_path":"/zrqHFQrF2HngVcEFRtW6sf1nIBD.jpg","original_title":"The Legend of Zorro","original_language":"en"},{"id":1669,"adult":false,"title":"The Hunt for Red October","video":false,"overview":"A new technologically-superior Soviet nuclear sub, the Red October, is heading for the U.S. coast under the command of Captain Marko Ramius. The American government thinks Ramius is planning to attack. Lone CIA analyst Jack Ryan has a different idea: he thinks Ramius is planning to defect, but he has only a few hours to find him and prove it - because the entire Russian naval and air commands are trying to find Ramius, too. The hunt is on!","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":4.9307,"vote_count":3551,"poster_path":"/yVl7zidse4KiWtGMqHFtZCx4X3N.jpg","release_date":"1990-03-02","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/5jCpCFrku6wmCZOYZWhHOC2j8IU.jpg","original_title":"The Hunt for Red October","original_language":"en"},{"id":1634,"adult":false,"title":"Free Willy","video":false,"overview":"When maladjusted orphan Jesse vandalizes a theme park, he is placed with foster parents and must work at the park to make amends. There he meets Willy, a young Orca whale who has been separated from his family. Sensing kinship, they form a bond and, with the help of kindly whale trainer Rae Lindley, develop a routine of tricks. However, greedy park owner Dial soon catches wind of the duo and makes plans to profit from them.","genre_ids":[10751,12,18],"popularity":3.4594,"vote_count":1923,"poster_path":"/9iBgd9gi9ztWiVcYSG6zl8wDFBN.jpg","release_date":"1993-07-16","vote_average":6.181,"backdrop_path":"/mXkUfzJfdWx9y4Zlm7wsvQ0uvYo.jpg","original_title":"Free Willy","original_language":"en"},{"id":1832,"adult":false,"title":"Dogma","video":false,"overview":"An abortion clinic worker with a special heritage is called upon to save the existence of humanity from being negated by two renegade angels trying to exploit a loophole and reenter Heaven.","genre_ids":[14,35,12],"popularity":3.7109,"vote_count":2762,"poster_path":"/dXXhveI3VO51C3VNzNrxYl2xbST.jpg","release_date":"1999-10-04","vote_average":6.925,"backdrop_path":"/nljRWpjfmqh5qYxcblFoazU5eYY.jpg","original_title":"Dogma","original_language":"en"},{"id":1771,"adult":false,"title":"Captain America: The First Avenger","video":false,"overview":"During World War II, Steve Rogers is a sickly man from Brooklyn who's transformed into super-soldier Captain America to aid in the war effort. Rogers must stop the Red Skull – Adolf Hitler's ruthless head of weaponry, and the leader of an organization that intends to use a mysterious device of untold powers for world domination.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":7.4408,"vote_count":22474,"poster_path":"/vSNxAJTlD0r02V9sPYpOjqDZXUK.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-22","vote_average":7.004,"backdrop_path":"/yFuKvT4Vm3sKHdFY4eG6I4ldAnn.jpg","original_title":"Captain America: The First Avenger","original_language":"en"},{"id":1724,"adult":false,"title":"The Incredible Hulk","video":false,"overview":"Scientist Bruce Banner scours the planet for an antidote to the unbridled force of rage within him: the Hulk. But when the military masterminds who dream of exploiting his powers force him back to civilization, he finds himself coming face to face with a new, deadly foe.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":10.4692,"vote_count":12497,"poster_path":"/gKzYx79y0AQTL4UAk1cBQJ3nvrm.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-12","vote_average":6.231,"backdrop_path":"/jPu8yiadqgzwFPGKJmGo637ASVP.jpg","original_title":"The Incredible Hulk","original_language":"en"},{"id":1865,"adult":false,"title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides","video":false,"overview":"When Jack crosses paths with a woman from his past, he's not sure if it's love...or if she's a ruthless con artist using him to find the fabled Fountain of Youth.","genre_ids":[12,28,14],"popularity":16.0581,"vote_count":14768,"poster_path":"/keGfSvCmYj7CvdRx36OdVrAEibE.jpg","release_date":"2011-05-15","vote_average":6.565,"backdrop_path":"/uzIGtyS6bbnJzGsPL93WCF1FWm8.jpg","original_title":"Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides","original_language":"en"},{"id":1891,"adult":false,"title":"The Empire Strikes Back","video":false,"overview":"The epic saga continues as Luke Skywalker, in hopes of defeating the evil Galactic Empire, learns the ways of the Jedi from aging master Yoda. But Darth Vader is more determined than ever to capture Luke. Meanwhile, rebel leader Princess Leia, cocky Han Solo, Chewbacca, and droids C-3PO and R2-D2 are thrown into various stages of capture, betrayal and despair.","genre_ids":[12,28,878],"popularity":7.6425,"vote_count":18093,"poster_path":"/nNAeTmF4CtdSgMDplXTDPOpYzsX.jpg","release_date":"1980-05-20","vote_average":8.392,"backdrop_path":"/aJCtkxLLzkk1pECehVjKHA2lBgw.jpg","original_title":"The Empire Strikes Back","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0371746","twitter_id":"iron_man","facebook_id":"ironman","wikidata_id":"Q192724","instagram_id":"","metacritic_id":"movie/iron-man","mydramalist_id":"147797","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/iron_man"},"social_ids":{"twitter":"ir